reviews.review_text: "This is a pretty hissy matrix sbd with lots of audience" yup, there are a lot of other straight up aud sources out there that will easily surpass this source for audio quality. For me personally I'll stick to those rather than grabbing this one.

still better than aud which lacks bass & echoy, i i love sounds WITH AUdience cheer !!!
Subject: Look, for awhile.... 
.
solid 3

Sounds fine to me with some AUD It almost seems like there was a microphone setup to capture the audience, and it was plumbed into the soundboard, like a ready-made matrix.   Anyhow, all good.  I especially like the quick Spanish flair put in at the end of Crazy Fingers.  Coolness Abides.
